Record Class MementoImpl

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
fr.istic.aco.editor.memento.MementoImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Memento<EngineImpl>
public record MementoImpl(EngineImpl state) extends Record implements Memento<EngineImpl>
Implementation of the Memento interface for the editor engine state. This class captures and stores a deep clone of the EngineImpl state to ensure immutability and encapsulation of the saved state.
